snippet.title: Wuthering Waves Latest Showcase Footage
snippet.description:
Introducing our latest in-game showcase! 
Experience the immersive newly added weather system that brings the game to life with realistic weather changes. Watch as the sun rises or sets, clouds gracefully float by, and rain gently falls.
#WutheringWaves
